{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d2392c91c","title":"捉住敌军才盾彻底击破胡宗南","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"168fdffe81","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":23,"articleId":"5d2392c91c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cf35657ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"捉住敌军才盾彻底击破胡宗南！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"b684797ab0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月23日）朱、张，彭，贺、任”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"85872f61f2","type":"paragraph","text":"现时敌军中发展着四种矛盾：第一种是抗日与“剩共”之间的矛盾；第二种是蒋军与东北军之间的矛盾：第三种是上级的严令进攻与下级的对红军热惧的矛盾，此种矛盾现在极大发展着：第四种是官长与士兵间的矛盾，此种矛盾以近日的物质困难与疲劳而加深。我们的任务是提住这些矛盾，更加团结一致，统一指挥，忍受与克服一切困难，不失每一个有利时机，灵活调动部队，准备连续战斗，坚决地各个击破进攻之敌，首先是彻底地击破胡宗南可","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"48e311c09a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"7a22bf284d","type":"paragraph","text":"二十三日十二时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"a39254f932","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给朱德和红军总政治委员张国煮，红军前敌总指挥兼政治委员、第一方面军司令员彭德怀等的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"4b78fb85bf","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]贺、任，指贺龙、任强时，当时分别任红军第二方面军总指挥和政治委员。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"},{"id":"bfe7fc0e9c","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“汇”总司令部第一路第二纵队司令兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c"}],"page":{"id":"4a77f077e3","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"5d2392c91c","start":19,"end":19}}}},"__N_SSG":true}